Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.39,0:00:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Doppel Ranger Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mua ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You got kicked, so fall down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.37,0:00:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,An evil empire plotting world domination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,won't be defeated that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.37,0:00:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always defeated\Nat the end of TV shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How is world domination going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.63,0:00:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy just won't go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But once you conquer the world,\Nyou'll have a lot of work to do after.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of world will you build?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:00:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just make a mess and that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.11,0:01:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna make a mess,\Nthat sounds a lot more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna quit being a Rainbow Ranger\Nand join an evil organization too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yay!\N-Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's all head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.25,0:01:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, we're leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.66,0:01:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.21,0:01:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay.\N-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.33,0:01:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-This way.\N-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten pretty hot, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It has.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Rosemary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she catch a cold this winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she was running around outside\Nwith her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd have such a terrible fever\Nevery year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, it was right around this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We rushed to a doctor\Nin the middle of the night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You walk around\Nwith an album of her photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I bet she's grown a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still growing. I wonder if her face\Nhas changed in this short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I'm confident
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that no matter how much she grows,\NI'll recognize her right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes, show her this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,These are newspaper clippings\Nand copies of reports
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,from when I shot and killed\Nthat young serial killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ask you to try and defend me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I killed someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to justify it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want that child to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder when I can meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to ask her again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to see if she wants to meet you or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home from work\Nby 9:00 p.m. every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard, you've recovered a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like when you were\Nstarting out as young police detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes are how they were\Nwhen we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,OFFENBACH, HESSEN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We can offer some perks\Nif you sign with us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've already enrolled with\Nanother insurance company.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you please reconsider, Mr. Liebert?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We are satisfied\Nwith our current insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And we don't have the luxury of\Npaying more for insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We just enrolled recently\Nwhen we moved here four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Four years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you move from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We lived in Brunnthal, near Mannheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Brunnthal, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that your hometown?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I lived there my whole life\Nuntil moving here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, ma'am,\Ndo you have any kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, our son is currently attending\Na college in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a college student?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I have\Nthe perfect insurance for young people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since he went to college in Munich,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we only get\Nthe occasional phone call from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how boys are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Boring, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I paid them a visit, Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I went to Johan's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:07:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was an extremely normal home\Nwith nothing out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you think, Richard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, based on my way of thinking\Nfrom my detective days,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing is more suspicious\Nthan when everything seems normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'll try looking into\NJohan's surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know there's something there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,At his preparatory school, Johan had
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,everything from superior grades\Nto great moral conduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I'm confident
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that no matter how much she grows,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll recognize her right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine that baby's face\Ngrowing up to look like Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,BRUNNTHAL TOWN HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is the birth certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan Wilhelm Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Born on February 9, 1976.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He was definitely born in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:08:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hertz!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times must I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No smoking in the town hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so harsh. Give me an ashtray.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a fire here\Nfour years ago, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The paperwork all burned\Nand caused a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you redo\Nall the paperwork when that happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we redid the paperwork\Nby having individuals fill them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're a small town,\Nso that was enough to get back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, thanks for coming, Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma came to you\Nand was looking for a man named Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no proof for what he was saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:10:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But if this person is the friend\Nwho inspired Peter Jürgens,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the serial killer\Nwho I am currently researching,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,then we'll have found a breakthrough\Nin this series of cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll get permission\Nto interview Jürgens as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show him this photo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and based on his reaction,\Nwe can prove Dr. Tenma's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He died?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The real Johan Liebert born in Brunnthal\Ndied when he was two years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the Liebert couple took advantage of\Nthe fire that burned the town hall records
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and refiled the papers with the stand-in
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to make it look\Nas if their dead son were alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-I believe so.\N-In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,what about the person\Ncurrently living as Johan Liebert?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in the world is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, as I said before,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave Johan's photo to Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hope an answer comes out from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we get dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I have to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:12:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you still have work\Nafter running around all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I may be getting a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be able to see my daughter again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's important is\Nto move forward, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, you've made a full recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosemary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course we can meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We can meet… anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard, it's Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jürgens, have you ever seen\Nthis young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you met him somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding your friend, Johan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you said he'd only send letters\Nand that you never met in person, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But Johan knew you very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I borrow a pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm not allowed to\Nhand you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The park.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The park.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The day after I killed someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm going to stop.\NI'll call it quits here."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought\Nas I went to the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He had many kids with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on,\NI forgot to turn on the tape recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you start over?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You should come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You should come too…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You should come too…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You should…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We met at Mr. Schuwald's home, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Johan Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I called many times,\Nbut you didn't pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So I came in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it go\Nafter you showed Jürgens the photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He died?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, just now at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tied up here\Nbecause of the police investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All because I carelessly handed him a pen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,an important witness ended up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But Dr. Reichwein,\Nthere is no doubt that his suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,was a reaction to Johan's photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll rush over\Nas soon as the investigation is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll contact Richard right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A college report?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm researching\Nthe Convention on the Rights of the Child
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,established by the U.N. in 1989.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like a drink, Richard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you don't drink alcohol anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes sense,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,since you executed that young man\Nwhile under the influence of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, although I was under the influence,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I still did something unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I want to ask you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The young man you killed\Nwas Stephen Joos, 17 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of crime did he commit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Young man, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:17:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That young man committed\Nheinous crimes at the age of 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine were raped and murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Two failed murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-So you executed him?\N-I didn't execute him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,\Nin Article 40 of the convention,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,a child is "to be presumed innocent\Nuntil proven guilty according to law."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I worked in\Nthe juvenile division before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then there's Article 37.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"Neither capital punishment\Nnor life imprisonment shall be imposed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,for offences committed by\Npersons below 18 years of age."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the convention
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is made up of basic human rights given to\Nboth children and adults in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When I killed him, it wasn't an execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a drunken mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I did something\Nthat can never be taken back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm even being punished societally--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, hold on a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to meet you\Nto write a report for college.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize if I've offended you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we take a walk for some fresh air?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have this whiskey?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind at night is still chilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't get a hold of Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he might get to meet his daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but I doubt he'd meet her\Nthis late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get a hold of him,\Ntell him to act carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm headed your way right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know Stephan Joos's history?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe he lived at an orphanage\Nin East Berlin when he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need to know more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a key point when talking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The orphanage he lived in\Nwas a horrible place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He was truly a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But imagine the terrible things\Nhe must've faced at the orphanage
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and how badly his mental state\Nmust have been mangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Convention on the Rights\Nof the Child Article 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"The right to life" and "the survival\Nand development of the child."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Article 8, "preserving\Nhis or her identity."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Article 19, "protection from\Nphysical or mental violence."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Such things were futile there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.21,0:19:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That place was like a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The place called Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you get to meet your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the person you were\Non the phone with earlier your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you meet her sometime tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,To write my college report.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The objective of being with Schuwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you were intoxicated\Nand shot the young man, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer my question first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,On that day, it's true\Nthat after you killed the young man,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you were seen drinking at a bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I've found,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,not a single person saw you drinking\Nbefore you killed that young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When you shot that young man,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you hadn't had any alcohol, had you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You were sober.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mind was clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You decided to execute him\Nand pulled the trigger with a clear mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you telling lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you lying to others?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you lying to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you confirm his crimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have the right to execute him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can make\Nyour sins disappear by lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What a serious crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.64,0:21:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is someone who committed\Nsuch a serious crime
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.85,0:21:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,going to meet his daughter,\Nacting like he made a full recovery?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Gillen? Is it you, Dr. Gillen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.51,0:22:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your patient, Richard Braun,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.97,0:22:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,has died.
